{"tid":555412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[老師渣車]教協：不涉專業操守，宜循法律追究！","createTime":"2018-02-09T11:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T12:24:46.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7bb366eea5c126aaa5038f74f0858538dc82df","tid":555412,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/194719_959e873facb21f9112df4e78ee01991d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F194719_959e873facb21f9112df4e78ee01991d.png&h=cf19d4d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸大學生爆粗 教協：絕不能接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n此次爭議，源於有浸大學生在向該校語文中心教職員表達不滿「普通話畢業要求」的訴求，<span style=\"color: red;\">期間有同學以粗言及不當態度辱罵教職員。我看過相關影片，如設身處地，相信亦會因學生的說話、態度和肢體動作而感到壓力。就算同學背後的理由和原意是好，這樣的表達方式看來也是不能接受的。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"468de9da09f3cae0ddbfe38217b4d28996e55642","tid":555412,"uid":13503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"教畜協會？"},{"pid":"e2774a986e5e885c95adc9e3ef0412d9108d2f02","tid":555412,"uid":49388,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"學生爆粗天怒人怨 人神共憤<br />\n教畜危險駕駛就WFC<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eae4b224d1b2832947c432f551f843b4e0f6b90","tid":555412,"uid":126977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"物以類聚 全部都係畜牲"},{"pid":"5eacaa16b95b9f99dff7a51e6b0f3ff12f10b8c8","tid":555412,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"香港啲雙重標準嘅廢中廢老點解唔快啲死左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b0fb3d26de113dc671add9249e8c443586b629","tid":555412,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0